{"pageid":324445,"pagename":"Perfect Verzik","title":"Perfect Verzik","displaytitle":"Perfect Verzik","revid":14282159,"properties":[{"name":"smw-semanticdata-status","value":""},{"name":"page_image_free","value":"Verzik_Vitur_(final_form).png"},{"name":"description","value":"Perfect Verzik is a master combat achievement which requires the player to defeat Verzik Vitur without anyone in the team taking avoidable damage from Verzik Vitur's attacks."}],"content":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox no-parenthesis-style infobox-task\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th class=\"infobox-header\" colspan=\"5\"><b>Perfect Verzik</b>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"infobox-padding\" colspan=\"5\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"infobox-full-width-content\" colspan=\"5\"><a href=\"/w/File:Verzik_Vitur_(final_form).png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Verzik Vitur (final form).png\" src=\"/images/thumb/Verzik_Vitur_%28final_form%29.png/250px-Verzik_Vitur_%28final_form%29.png?f9733\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"250\" height=\"228\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/Verzik_Vitur_%28final_form%29.png/375px-Verzik_Vitur_%28final_form%29.png?f9733 1.5x, /images/thumb/Verzik_Vitur_%28final_form%29.png/500px-Verzik_Vitur_%28final_form%29.png?f9733 2x\" data-file-width=\"1592\" data-file-height=\"1449\" /></a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"infobox-padding\" colspan=\"5\">\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Released\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/w/21_July\" title=\"21 July\">21 July</a> <a href=\"/w/2021\" title=\"2021\">2021</a> (<a href=\"/w/Update:Combat_Achievements\" title=\"Update:Combat Achievements\">Update</a>)\n</td></tr>\n\n\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Task\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\">Defeat Verzik Vitur without anyone in the team taking damage from Verzik Vitur's attacks other than her spider form's correctly prayed against regular magical and ranged attacks.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/w/Members\" title=\"Members\">Members</a>\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\">Yes\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Area\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/w/Theatre_of_Blood\" title=\"Theatre of Blood\">Theatre of Blood</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Reward\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\">None\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/w/Achievement_Diary\" title=\"Achievement Diary\">Diary</a>\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/w/Combat_Achievements\" title=\"Combat Achievements\">Combat Achievements</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Tier\n</th>\n<td colspan=\"3\"><a href=\"/w/Combat_Achievements/Master\" title=\"Combat Achievements/Master\">Master</a>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr>\n<td class=\"infobox-padding\" colspan=\"5\">\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<p><b>Perfect Verzik</b> is a <a href=\"/w/Combat_Achievements/Master\" title=\"Combat Achievements/Master\">master combat achievement</a> which requires the player to defeat <a href=\"/w/Verzik_Vitur\" title=\"Verzik Vitur\">Verzik Vitur</a> without anyone in the team taking avoidable damage from Verzik Vitur's attacks.\n</p><p>Specifically, players are <b>not</b> allowed to take damage from:\n</p>\n<ul><li>Magic and ranged attacks during phases 1 and 2</li>\n<li>Damage from pillar falling</li>\n<li>Nylocas explosions</li>\n<li>Verzik's bounce attack during phase 2\n<ul><li>If no damage is taken, this will not invalidate the run</li></ul></li>\n<li>Lightning attack final hit</li>\n<li>Ranged or magic attacks during phase 3 that are not correctly prayed against</li>\n<li>Being stuck in a web when it expires</li>\n<li>Yellow projectile when not shielded</li>\n<li>Green bomb attack without bouncing it to other players as many times as possible</li></ul>\n<p>Players may take damage from:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Nylocas_Athanatos\" title=\"Nylocas Athanatos\">Nylocas Athanatos</a> landing</li>\n<li>Lightning attack if it will continue to target another player</li>\n<li>Green bomb attack if it will continue to target another player or it cannot be bounced further</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Changes\">Changes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Perfect_Verzik?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Perfect_Verzik?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Changes\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable mw-collapsible sortable\" style=\"max-width:800px\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Date\n</th>\n<th class=\"unsortable\">Changes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td data-sort-value=\"4 August 2021\"><a href=\"/w/4_August\" title=\"4 August\">4&#160;August</a>&#160;<a href=\"/w/2021\" title=\"2021\">2021</a><br />(<a href=\"/w/Update:New_Client_Features:_Milestone_2\" title=\"Update:New Client Features: Milestone 2\">update</a>)\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>The \"Perfect Verzik\" task will no longer fail if players take damage from Verzik's green ball attack, providing it was successfully bounced to another player.\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"Combat Achievements\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" id=\"navbox-title\"><div class=\"navbox-title-name-notplain\"><div class=\"navbar\" style=\"float:left;text-align:left;width:6em\"><div class=\"plainlinks noprint\" style=\"background-color:transparent;padding:0;font-weight:normal;font-size:xx-small;white-space:nowrap\"><a href=\"/w/Template:Combat_Achievements\" title=\"Template:Combat Achievements\"><span title=\"View this template\">v</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template_talk:Combat_Achievements\"><span title=\"Discussion about this template\">d</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\