 be bounced further\n\n==Changes==\n{{Subject changes header}}\n{{Subject changes\n|date = 4 August 2021\n|update = New Client Features: Milestone 2\n|poll =\n|change = The \"Perfect Verzik\" task will no longer fail if players take damage from Verzik's green ball attack, providing it was successfully bounced to another player.\n}}\n{{Subject changes footer}}\n\n{{Combat Achievements}}"}